description.en: LadderCaster is a Solana-based strategy NFT game and player-to-player market that combines elements of classic board games with blockchain and NFT technologies. Players earn their way through thirty levels across a dynamic boardscape with an unlimited number of SpellCasters and race their way to the top. LadderCaster’s economy is player-owned, where users truly have all the power to seamlessly buy, sell, or trade any resources or assets earned through playing.
